name: Andrews-Curtis conjecture enumeration
tagline: Fork of http://www.stevens.edu/algebraic/downloads.php with added routines realted to the Andrews-Curtis conjecture
body:
Currently this page only contains instructions on how to reproduce results from [D. Panteleev, A. Ushakov - CONJUGACY SEARCH PROBLEM AND THE ANDREWS-CURTIS CONJECTURE](http://example.com). If you need description for some other CRAG modules, please refer to [https://github.com/stevens-crag/crag]

There is also newer and independent implementation at [https://github.com/dpantele/acc], but currently it completely lacks any documentation and does not have all routins reimplemented there.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
